[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating native image mutability**\n\nI’m considering the challenges of mutating a public final static field in a native image. It seems like using `Unsafe.objectFieldOffset` might lead to errors with static finals, especially if they're build-time initialized. Reflection might not be a viable alternative here, either. Plus, there's the context of Native Image on Linux, and JNA could have its own substitutions. Overall, I think the hack could introduce some problematic scenarios.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0fb63b68099e23620169f9030b7440819ca723bd7b5b34f0bd\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-QMaSrOClqcfF8pmf5hDf18aLL5vX-FqsnysPlrNdCd5kZqqVXc0DqFCzOwdfPGymHiRPyYyQW2qb2XQ7uEeSXs-piaOwUC4V_UfWPc1ieuv-zJiZe3pWeiXBA8AwwnPRO3Jor58Z4wXXZIVNYihPPdYz3famkM0AnwkL836RhyLFIQtLnmJKHuN0Q7Ytjy3EQfRTfYXgnDLUV_5oU0q-oKjjJEATHq7OieTSGDoit6OrBMRFHKzKp67fLkwW94ghTEaY2GfVBkZ0GWs0cVAl_dkidpCmHDJSsIm739tm-esZz9r9nXBcSHjwsqWTOWW4fJbW6QtQdFGZCKVMZLvZKE3odJoTfiw5wWuK1fvMfDozvAlZ-d93c14ndRH3G3zdbOHeXvH3KjOialQ7Choo4f-ex4vLg6aVoFu_QdzEx7ghbFENafCgenecOJsF-LvJ-PMdnKukhB2ZOR8j1oejUMDoX5i9u3YGGhoBHHf53hwDvxVofAPgAJ2ULY_7Qoj4O1EJnEPsWM7XMolFy_iMGYXzfOAICW9y5V9ropGV8_r9rl350JkBAp6W7q67EFGxoxoy7_HTcAwpuCoidzKT-PsJJuHPBqRu74uX7ehT46u8qR9Ps2XmltrUbQCQXtPhNePpq1Wb94qdBB2-ve22qB6kRTU4LCk8kuI_gkGRyi18Wc-YV4jQFxH78OT-7T_sOgfEDC83lphSvPUNO2OI5JHEB2m5IjbTmcXGmt726_X_GNlOVKtbdHtOUrjdmqbLBtGYd6pRkzH5cJu3oeu94lZ-dBm-SyjvUMMB7ecF2ljE4GYregyUXUDuakf2FvNk_I1tIuUfpqzQd42SPa_WjPGHP95bGTlPrqYqO_hlJGipeFDiXfF0QpFSpNVYmrv5WnwbQXyykRK8GLnGsFleAyCmzJKth7ooqa0TCVrpg-FX9okwrtnMMFbGvexH_UQF-EdMxZUd4vrWIjKRiZms7F9gcF9MJrCMVVASEVfHrSDgnkjfEvZMiiLIE9cLSWzC7lCfnWUXrUKmDL8PU33eKQKQ1xhAH9AROYt2DpCwHHZaQ1DTIjWuTdO_hNEggZUw1olZKq6Iy84lUs09Yl1r98obSsGyvDJ97r3xswNBwheQHFHlNenFffGNEUxWw1SNBnOsaW706dvT8gYZO9y9bS_ykRj7dFNrtonDfNnHnSvo10M0vG61L6NlJseQZotZ1rV0pDG4cPACpUTbbae8eYavxEko4FQ-l3xfyOc